description: Capacity Building project with the Ministry of Marine Resources to Improve Fishing Communities Livelihoods

subproject.corporate outcome: Enabling Climate Change Adpatation policy established, Sustinable Land Managment mainstreamed into sectors.
subproject.description: The project outputs include promotion of local fish markets, development of community based fisheries production, accreditation of Fish Quality Control Laboratory (FQCL), srengthening institutional capacity of the Ministry and Hirgigo Fisheries Training Centre.
subproject.title: Improving Fishing Communities
